OL,3,CMan arrested after four-vehicle
OL,4,Ccollision closed major road
OL,6,FA 31-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of dangerous driving after a
OL,8,Ffour-vehicle collision closed one of
OL,9,FJersey's main roads for several hours.
OL,11,FThe incident happened at around 1pm on
OL,12,FWednesday (1 July) on the Esplanade in
OL,13,FSt Helier, at the traffic lights
OL,14,Fjunction with Gloucester Street.
OL,16,FPeople were asked to avoid the area
OL,17,Fand there was heavy traffic congestion
OL,18,Fwhile emergency services responded to
OL,19,Fthe collision between a coach, car,
OL,20,Fvan and motorbike.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
