CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783698492
OL,3,CMan arrested after four-vehicle
OL,4,Ccollision closed major road
OL,6,FThe injuries are believed to be minor,
OL,7,Fwith one driver taken to the nearby
OL,8,FGeneral Hospital as a precaution.
OL,10,FAccess was blocked from La Route de la
OL,11,FLiberation roundabout and the
OL,12,Funderpass on to the Esplanade
OL,13,Fwestbound for several hours.
OL,15,FThe road has now fully reopened, with
OL,16,Fthe States of Jersey Police thanking
OL,17,Fpeople for their patience.
OL,19,FMeanwhile, they are appealing for
OL,20,Fwitnesses to come forward.
