OL,3,CMan arrested after four-vehicle
OL,4,Ccollision closed major road
OL,6,FThe vehicles involved were a blue
OL,7,FVolkswagen Transporter van, a yellow
OL,8,FSuzuki motorbike, a silver Audi TT car
OL,9,Fand a blue Leyland Swift Tantivy coach.
OL,11,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,12,Fcontact police on 01534 612612 or
OL,13,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,14,F111.
